{"type": "article", "id": 29032, "title": "带上它们，过个优雅的下雨天｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2016-07-02T07:20:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5833, "name": "Hunter"}, {"id": 19682, "name": "Rains"}, {"id": 29679, "name": "雨具"}, {"id": 29680, "name": "The Arrivals"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 533, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703181203quhE9e0NYHgs75Ln.jpg", "contents": "\r\n\r\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\r\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<p>每到炎炎夏日都希望下一场雨来冲刷烦躁之气，而真遇到一场暴雨，又常常被搞得狼狈不堪。也许你还在吐槽 30 年未变的雨衣雨鞋的设计，但在一些多雨的地方，它们已经变得时尚且优雅。英国的雨具公司&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/4972.html\">Hunter </a>早已进入了秀场，在设计上吸收时尚和潮流文化，就像一个高端服饰品牌。我们在这周推荐一些有设计或者时尚的雨具，在国内，这似乎还是一个没有被重视的市场。</p>\r\n<h2>Original Tour Short Wellington Boots by Hunter</h2>\r\n<p>威灵顿靴的历史可以追溯到 17 世纪，这种早期用来保护士兵膝盖不受伤害的靴子在今天已经成为了日常以及雨天出行常见的时尚单品。英国著名制靴品牌 Hunter 的 Original 是旗下的经典系列，短靴由轻便、可折叠的橡胶手工制成。它可以轻松地卷成一团，无论是通勤还是出门旅行，雨季在包里备着准没错。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.hunterboots.com/womens-short-wellingtons/womens-original-tour-short-wellington-boots/black/2766\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 75 英镑。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181147p4haIcV2Ti7ebrPR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181147i5GIAh18c9Yg2NyQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031811481GWkLMAcdONYRvsQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181148w3MfcQpiWA2gsUaL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181148NAqC8c5QFUtoIOHh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181149Nd0ljQeuRvZbq6og.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Häring Poncho by The Arrivals</h2>\r\n<p>风雨交加的时候，撑一把雨伞出门有可能还会让你淋得更狼狈，穿上雨披是一个更保险的选择。纽约的服装公司 The Arrivals 推出了一款用防水的弹性纤维和橡胶斜纹织物制成的雨披 Häring Poncho，双面都能够防水防风，造型上也不失时尚。设计师们根据自己穿戴时的体验增加了一些贴心的细节：雨披左右各有一道拉链让人更方便地取用口袋里的物品；被设计成棒球帽风格的兜帽在遇到迎面而来的风雨时可以提供更好的保护。这是它的<a href=\"http://thearrivals.com/womens-haring-poncho\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 245 美元。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181150GE21CfPIBD6XYzqS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66704545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181150E5nPmJ0gSWzCs7cj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69772727\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181151JsrBGgxaIz5O6UKW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031811510jmOCv5RV2ZiMLGs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74318182\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\r\n<h2>Msn Bag by RAINS</h2>\r\n<p>遇到一场突如其来的大雨，除了担心自己的身体以外，你一定有为包里的贵重物品而提心吊胆的经历，如果你也觉得把包背到胸前不是什么解决办法，不妨来看看丹麦品牌 RAINS 推出的 Msn 背包。背包采用聚酯纤维制成，具有良好的防水性能。正面有两个搭扣，打开后就是一个宽敞的收纳空间，日常通勤使用绰绰有余。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.rains.dk/collections/bags-accessories/products/msn-bag\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 67.09 欧元。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181152Gpi1DFLIrQTU3qWX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181152wyrx9kZGHihMWKQO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181153GubTOHKEw6W2CYoR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181153h0YAUxeQJzgG8Rio.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181154mys2NAxuqlzjZCwG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<h2>MOSEBACKE by Stutterheim</h2>\r\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"stutterheim.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stutterheim</a> 是瑞典做高端雨衣的品牌，成立于 2010 年，所有衣服或帽子都是手工缝制的。MOSEBACKE 系列是女士的雨衣，呈 A 字形，看起来很宽敞，如果不戴帽子并将衣服敞开，就像是一件很酷的风衣，这种跳出传统雨衣的做法就像 Hunter一样，拥有时尚的特征。这套雨衣有墨绿、浅棕、黑、白等 8 种颜色，适合各个场合，<a href=\"https://stutterheim.com/jp/mosebacke-light-sand?affsrc=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">这里是购买链接</a>。<br></p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181154IlCvRhzStjFGAn1J.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.82346939\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181155gBlDQsSCAMOb41X3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50491803\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181156Mkq6w2WoLunYcp3s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.82346939\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031811568LvAQZlsyPUWw27o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\r\n<h2>Boncho by Vanmoof </h2>\r\n<p>这件雨衣是荷兰自行车品牌 Vanmoof 专为骑行者设计的，它尽可能避免人和车被雨打湿。车把手和手的部分有伞骨固定，降低因为吹风将雨衣掀开的可能，而它穿上的弧度和长度都能有效遮挡雨水或方便自然滑落。它更重要的设计是快速收放，利用了遮光板收放的原理，可以将雨衣收成一个圆环，方便旅行时携带。它目前已完成<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/boncho/boncho-the-bike-poncho/updates\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹</a>和生产。<br></p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181157DbgIOjmx2cpBwSR9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181158yg650OwQofPd7eqp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61858974\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181158o03mkhnXx8gM6E1s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53098291\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181159myuRltCV5osJQ0Ac.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52564103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181159Xa6ep4JERD5FkwyS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40705128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181200CbP4g39soBaHSGVz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.28418803\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>1205/02 bag by rains</h2>\r\n<p class=\"\">这家丹麦品牌 <a href=\"www.rains.dk\" rel=\"nofollow\">rains</a> 也是一家专门做雨具的品牌，产品包括雨衣和配件，种类非常丰富。它们的包都用防水材料，针对了不同的情景，也很有设计感。比如这款手提包是用来旅行的，两头都有锁扣带来塑形，整体样式传统但看起来大方且能适应很多场合，售价 499DKK，这里是<a href=\"https://www.rains.dk/collections/bags-accessories/products/bag?variant=16742944065\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>。<br></p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181200GTb9e1tJWLm6VnAv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181201yx1KPWVbdh4gwYr5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181201Is2Zh5Lmf9Dkody7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181202ZCb0xrO5THU3WS2M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181202e13pLwx4cEmKOf6T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"\">题图来自：视觉中国</p>\r\n\r\n"}